structure.unit: STATE AND AREA PLANNING -- REGIONAL DEVELOPMENT

law.history: Repealed 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 253, sec. 13, effective July 15, 1982. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 359, sec. 2. -- Created 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 248, sec. 5, effective June 16, 1960.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Effect on existing master plans -- Local legislative body to state reasons for overriding recommendation of area planning commission.
